#. Tag: para
#: session_api.xml:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a parent is passed to <literal>persist()</literal>, all children are "
"passed to <literal>persist()</literal>"
msgstr ""
"親が <literal>persist()</literal> に渡されたならば、 すべての子は "
